  "text": "We evaluate CBARS performance with various clustering techniques deployed in phase 2. The algorithm implements Weka [CITATION_1] clustering techniques, namely k-means, EM and DBScan. Experimentally, clustering accuracy has a direct influence on the system performance. Therefore, we apply the EM clustering in all our experiments unless otherwise stated.",
